OL,3,CFailed asylum seeker guilty of
OL,4,Cattempted terror attack on Israeli
OL,5,Cembassy
OL,7,FA failed asylum seeker has been found
OL,8,Fguilty of trying to break into the
OL,9,FIsraeli embassy in London to launch a
OL,10,Fknife attack.
OL,12,FKuwait-born Abdullah Albadri, 34, was
OL,13,Ftackled by armed police after he
OL,14,Fhurdled over an embassy fence in
OL,15,FKensington, west London, armed with
OL,16,Ftwo knives last May.
OL,18,FOn Friday, a jury at the Old Bailey
OL,19,Ffound him guilty of preparation of
OL,20,Fterrorist acts and possession of two
OL,21,Fbladed articles.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
