PN,31802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1777719769
OL,3,CFailed asylum seeker guilty of
OL,4,Cattempted terror attack on Israeli
OL,5,Cembassy
OL,7,FHe was remanded in custody and will be
OL,8,Fsentenced at a later date.
OL,10,FOn April 28 last year, CCTV showed
OL,11,FAlbadri walking for an hour from
OL,12,FKilburn in north-west London to the
OL,13,Fembassy, with his head covered by dark
OL,14,Fsunglasses and a distinctive red and
OL,15,Fwhite headscarf.
OL,17,FJurors were told he tried to enter the
OL,18,Fgrounds to "exact revenge" for the
OL,19,Fkilling of children in Gaza.
OL,26,@zD@LOUzD@ZO]
