PN,31803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1777719769
OL,3,CFailed asylum seeker guilty of
OL,4,Cattempted terror attack on Israeli
OL,5,Cembassy
OL,7,FThe court heard Albadri had been
OL,8,Frefused asylum after arriving in the
OL,9,FUK in small boats in 2021 and again in
OL,10,FApril 2025.
OL,12,FThe defendant, who is from Kuwait's
OL,13,Fminority Bedoon community, said he had
OL,14,Fbeen jailed and mistreated for
OL,15,Fcampaigning for human rights in his
OL,16,Fnative country.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
