PN,31804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1777719769
OL,3,CFailed asylum seeker guilty of
OL,4,Cattempted terror attack on Israeli
OL,5,Cembassy
OL,7,FAfter being arrested at the embassy,
OL,8,Fhe told police: "I wanna make a crime
OL,9,Finside there, why are you stopping me?
OL,10,FWhy are you stopping from making
OL,11,Fcrimes?"
OL,13,FHe went on to complain: "Why didn't
OL,14,Fyou let me in?"
OL,16,FBefore being put into a police van,
OL,17,FAlbadri was heard on police body-worn
OL,18,Fvideo to say: "You know it's just a
OL,19,Fmessage, yeah.
OL,26,@pD@QOUsD@HO]uD@YOUvD@OO]zD@OOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
