PN,31805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1777719769
OL,3,CFailed asylum seeker guilty of
OL,4,Cattempted terror attack on Israeli
OL,5,Cembassy
OL,7,F"They need to stop this f****** war on
OL,8,Fchildren.
OL,10,F"We need to live in harmony because
OL,11,Fthe children who live there, it's all
OL,12,Fthe same.
OL,14,F"We are living in the same Earth, it's
OL,15,Fnot a faraway place..."
OL,17,FAlbadri later denied preparing an act
OL,18,Fof terrorism, saying the knives were
OL,19,Ffor "personal use" as he was homeless.
