OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FGiving evidence at his trial, he
OL,13,Finsisted he never intended to enter
OL,14,Fthe embassy grounds or harm anyone,
OL,15,Fand that his actions were a protest.
