PN,31807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1777719769
OL,3,CFailed asylum seeker guilty of
OL,4,Cattempted terror attack on Israeli
OL,5,Cembassy
OL,7,FFollowing the verdict, Bethan David,
OL,8,Fhead of the Crown Prosecution Service
OL,9,FCounter terrorism division, said:
OL,10,F"Abdullah Albadri deliberately armed
OL,11,Fhimself, concealed his identity and
OL,12,Fattempted to climb into a diplomatic
OL,13,Fsite while carrying knives.
OL,15,F"The evidence showed planning and
OL,16,Fpreparation, and that his actions were
OL,17,Fdriven by an intention to use violence
OL,18,Fto make a political statement.
